## 阶段交接 — Plan → Build

在调用 ship 之前，写入 **结构化交接** 让 build 阶段获得紧凑摘要，
而不必重新阅读完整计划。

写入 `TASK_DIR/handoff-plan.json`，结构如下：
```json
{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "source_phase": "plan",
  "target_phase": "build",
  "task_id": "task-NNN",
  "summary": "<2-4 句摘要：要构建什么、关键方案、约束>",
  "decisions": [{"what": "...", "why": "...", "classification": "mechanical|taste"}],
  "risks": [{"description": "...", "mitigation": "...", "severity": "low|medium|high"}],
  "open_items": [{"description": "...", "owner": "builder|user", "priority": "high|medium|low"}],
  "artifacts_produced": ["plan.md"],
  "scope_changes": [],
  "created_at": "<ISO 8601 UTC>"
}
```

然后更新 `workflow-state.json` → `artifacts.handoff` 为 `"handoff-plan.json"`。

如果 `workflow-state.json` 不存在，跳过更新 — handoff 为可选增强。

---

## 执行

Review gate 已通过。调用 `/harness-ship` 执行完整的
build → eval → ship → PR 管线。

Ship 会派遣同样的 5 个角色（architect、product-owner、engineer、
qa、project-manager）以 `code-eval` 模式进行评审阶段。
